    replace those coords with the coords of the portal.
    /////////////////second way//////////////////////
    look what id the portal is by exemple if the id is 7324
    open up your client.java until u look a code looking like

makeGlobalObject(3333, 3253, 7324, 0, 10);//portal and u yust delte the code and compile and voila ur donne
